# Canonical author identities for this repository.
#
# GitHub honours `.mailmap` for the contributors graph and the per-repo
# stats. The email-only form below is the most reliable: any commit-author
# or `Co-Authored-By` trailer carrying the matched email gets re-attributed,
# regardless of the display name on it.
#
# Format reference: https://git-scm.com/docs/gitmailmap

# Claude Code (Anthropic's CLI assistant) — co-author trailer attribution
# folds into the human who ran the tool.
<sumit.das@disseqt.ai> <noreply@anthropic.com>

# GitHub web-edit identity folds into the local-git identity.
<sumit.das@disseqt.ai> <sumit-disseqt@users.noreply.github.com>

# Display-name fallbacks (covers any commit where the name field is the
# variant but the email is already canonical).
Sumit Das <sumit.das@disseqt.ai> Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
Sumit Das <sumit.das@disseqt.ai> Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Sumit Das <sumit.das@disseqt.ai> claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Sumit Das <sumit.das@disseqt.ai> sumit-disseqt <sumit.das@disseqt.ai>
